explanation: The contract contains no language requiring the parties to refrain from exporting or re-exporting Confidential Information in violation of applicable export control laws. Because this obligation is absent, the contract does not meet the rule’s requirement.
rule: Require that neither party will export or re-export any Confidential Information in violation of applicable export control laws.
exampleLanguage: Each party agrees not to export or re-export any Confidential Information in violation of applicable export control laws.
